Basic Qualifications ( Educational, Other Skills )
* LLB/LLM
* Labour Laws, Corporate laws and various other aspects relating to mergers and acquisitions
* FEMA regulations, joint ventures, reorganization, regulatory issues
* Organised and methodical with the ability to work to strict deadlines and schedules
* Self motivated, with ability to function with limited supervision at a demanding pace
* Very good communication skills including legal/technical drafting
* Very good interpersonal skills
* Good analytical and process skills
Job Content
* Advisory and legal consulting
* Independently handling legal, financial, commercial aspects and compliance in relation to transactions
* Legal drafting of Transactions, Mergers & Acquisitions and Joint Ventures
* Coordination between SKP and Law firms
* Process research and development
